text: AlunaGeorge are Aluna Francis and George Reid, two electronic musicians from London. ==History== In 2009 Francis and Reid met when Reid remixed Francis' band My Toys Like Me's song "Sweetheart". AlunaGeorge's first album Body Music was released by Island Records. ==Other websites== *Official website Category:2009 establishments in the United Kingdom Category:Electronic music groups
